2026-05-11T07:47:58.5500486Z 12    <!--
2026-05-11T07:47:58.5500865Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-11T07:47:58.5501222Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
